HEADWORD: Water cell
<hw>Wa"ter cell`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A cell containing water;
specifically <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, one of the cells or chambers in which
water is stored up in the stomach of a camel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

